CM_ "Version:V1.1.0,Date:2025/6/12,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:韩胜明设变,Description:(PSM)1、报文VIU_3A4中，新增发送信号ADS_ZeGrvySeatPreCrash，VIU1_CABIN新增发送，PSM新增接收。;
Version:V1.3.0,Date:2025/8/29,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:向宇设变,Description:(PSM)1、新增报文PSM_0x5FB，报文中新增信号PSM_ZeroGravityUnfoldBtn，PSM_ZeroGravityFoldBtn，PSM_ZeroGravityFoldSt，PSM_SeatAngleMotPosn，均是PSM发，VIU1_CABIN收；
2、报文VIU_3A4中新增VIU_PsmZeroGravityFoldFunSet，VIU1_CABIN发，PSM收；
3、报文RDS_345中新增RDS_RLSecRowSeatHeatLvlSet，RDS_RLSecRowSeatVentLvlSet，RDS_RRSecRowSeatHeatLvlSet，RDS_RRSecRowSeatVentLvlSet，均是RDS发，VIU1_CABIN收；
4、新增报文VIU_347，报文中新增信号VIU_LRSM_HeatgSts，VIU_LRSM_VentnSts，VIU_RRSM_HeatgSts，VIU_RRSM_VentnSts，均是VIU1_CABIN发，RDS收；
5、新增DSM节点；;
Version:V2.0.0,Date:2025/9/23,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:高永建设变,Description:(PSM)1、报文PSM_0x5FB中新增PSM_ZeroGravityforbiddenReasonSt，PSM发，VIU1_CABIN收；
2、报文VIU_DSM_0x39A中新增VIU_DrvrSeatLegSupportMotPosnStepSet，VIU_DrvrSeatLegExtnMotPosnStepSet，VIU0_IP发，DSM收；;
Version:V2.0.0,Date:2025/9/26,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:高永建设变,Description:(PSM)1、DSM,PSM取消加热状态信号，涉及DSM,PSM,VIU0_IP,VIU1_CABIN；;
Version:V2.1.0,Date:2025/11/3,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:徐雅军设变,Description:(PSM)1、报文VIU_CDC_0x3AA中信号VIU_BackLiBriSet新增PSM收，涉及PSM,VIU1_CABIN；;
Version:V3.1.0,Date:2025/12/6,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:胡新安设变,Description:(PSM)1、新增信号PSM_AP_hall_cushionAngle，PSM_AP_current_cushionAngle，PSM_ApTrigReasoncushionAngle；
2、新增报文PSM_0x63F，报文中新增信号PSM_ApTrigReasonTilt，PSM_APTrigReasoncurrent，PSM_APTrigReasonhal，涉及PSM,VIU1_CABIN；;
Version:V5.2.0,Date:2026/4/17,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:胡新安设变,Description:(PSM)1、PSM_0x63F修改为PSM_0x2A7，周期调整为50ms，涉及PSM,VIU1_CABIN；;
Version:V5.2.0,Date:2026/4/20,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:胡新安设变,Description:(PSM)1、新增报文DSM_AP_DiffCurrent，PSM_AP_DiffCurrent，涉及DSM,PSM；;
 ";

